description:
The Bedbug Bible Gang | Old Testament Heroes & Prophets | Episode 27 | All About Abraham

Part one of this three-part episode features three stories about Abraham: Abraham's Big Move, Pillar of Salt, and Abraham and Isaac.

Three previously unreleased episodes of the Bedbug bible Gang television series. The first program tells All About Abraham who faithfully followed God his whole life long. Next, God's people were saved by a heroine named Esther in Esther Fest. And finally, those often overlooked heroes, the prophets, get their say in Prophet Parade. This delightful program combines 3-D computer animation with illustrations and live-action puppets to make learning Bible stories fun for children.

Director: Larry Neeb
Starring: Lanette Marquardt, David Mead
